sentences.sContent: However, to do so, it must find an unoccupied territory and a member of the opposite sex with which to mate.
sentences.sContent_eng: However, to do so, it must find an unoccupied territory and a member of the opposite sex with which to mate.
sentences.sCn: 然而，要想成为领头狼，必须找到一块未被占领的领地和一头能够与之交配的异性狼。

synos.tran: 空闲的；没人住的；未占领的；无人占领的

trans.tranOther: a seat, house, room etc that is unoccupied has no one in it
